nodes.text: The wharf was a location on Level 1313 of Coruscant's sprawling underworld. It had an underground lake, speeder docks, and a place for people to sit and eat food. Ahsoka Tano and Trace Martez got a meal there after dealing with some dangerous binary loadlifters Trace's sister Rafa had been hired to work on. Rafa later met them there, revealing that she had sold the droids to the Twi'lek who had hired her anyways, despite the danger, which Tano and Trace were not pleased about.
The wharf first appeared in the Star Wars: The Clone Wars seventh season episode "Gone with a Trace."
